item.title: Need help please?
item.dc:creator: @Mimz Mimz
item.description:
@Mimz wrote:

It means either choose another name for your server, or change the title… Try putting ~~'s next to it, or changing something about it like say the name is MimzScape, it would then be M!mz$c@p3, or something like that…
